<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.1">
<l>neṟintakaruṅ kuḻalmaṭavāy niṉṉaṭiyēṉ viṇṇappam</l>
<l>ceṟintamaṇi muṭiccaṉakaṉ cilaiyiṟuttu niṉaikkoṇarnta</l>
<l>taṟintaracu kaḷaikaṭṭa varuntavattō ṉiṭaivilaṅka</l>
<l>ceṟintacilai koṭutavattaic citaittatumō raṭaiyāḷam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lady with curly dark tresses! Salutations! I am your servant.</l>
<l>[He] broke the bow of Janaka, with a crown crowded with jewels,</l>
<l rend="indent">knowing that [he would] attain you;</l>
<l>and, having taken the thick bow in order to obstruct</l>
<l>the way of the one with rare tapas who robbed the kings,</l>
<l rend="indent">[he] destroyed [that] tapas.</l>
<l>[This] is one proof.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
